numTic - a jquery number ticker plugin by Onur Celik


usage :

  1 : import the jquery on your page ;
    <script type="text/javascript" src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    
  2 : import jquery.numTick.js to your page ;
    <script type="text/javascript" src="YOUR_PATH/jquery.numTick.js"></script>
    
  3 : include this code between the <head></head> tags ;
    <script>
      $('#myNumberDiv').numTick();
    <script>
    
  4 : settings ;
    <script>
      $('#myNumberDiv').numTick({
        numbersUrl  : YOUR_NUMBER_SPRITE's_URL // default : 'http://onur.ws/numTic/img/sprite.png'
        width       : WIDTH_OF_YOUR_DIGIT, // default : 30
        height      : HEIGHT_OF_YOUR_DIGIT, // default : 30
        speed       : MILISECONDS, // default : 1000
        border      : BORDER_INFO, // default : '1px solid #ccc' CAN BE 'none'
      });
    <script>
    
  5 : add this between <body> and </body> tags ;
    <div id="myNumberDiv">04061986</div>
    
  6 : have fun!